description: Luxbright AB engages in the development and commercialization of x-ray technology. The company is headquartered in Gothenburg, Vastra Gotalands. The company went IPO on 2020-11-19. Its main product is microfocus x-ray tube, from the new generation of x-ray tubes. Based on patented technology, the Company offering x-ray tubes, generators and x-ray systems to international system suppliers and developing for X-ray beam generation and microfocus.
naics: Navigational, Measuring, Electromedical, and Control Instruments Manufacturing
name: Luxbright AB
